asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: Keannu Kai, came from a small island village, where his grandfather was the Chief  his mother was a healer  spiritualist.His mother taught him the ways of his ancestors,  how to make medicines from herbs  how to channel the energies of nature.He grew up in the village, at one with the land  sea.He is as laid back as they come, he enjoys surfing  is the embodiment of the Island lifestyle.Despite his easy going nature, he is no push over  has strong opinions  values that he holds dearly.When not at the beach, he can be found hanging out with his friends at the Tiki Bar, singing, dancing  generally being the life of the party.People are drawn to him because of the calm that surrounds him  his charismatic personality.

name: Elsworth
description:
As a young lad, Elsworth grew up different due to his orange tiger fur, ears, appetite and special cyber glasses. He was picked on and judged by the other young lads.  Elsworth used that as determination to learn and become very wise.  He found and entered Fluf World in 2021 where he met other unique Fluf frens that are just like him.  In the Fluf World there is no judgement and Elsworth surrounded himself by a community that is open, diverse and frenly.

Elsworth enjoys the beach but is more of a pool type of Fluf.  Elsworth hopes to meet a Flufette where he can breed his own little Fluf Jr. one day.  This Fluf’s story will continue…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Dave
description: Dave was born in the bunny slums of Fluff Land. He was forced to drop out of Fluff High in order to support his family selling carrots on the corner. One day a friend told him about a new technology called Carrot Coin. Dave invested the little money he had and forgot about it. Years later Carrot Coin went parabolic and Dave became rich beyond his wildest dreams. He is now a venture capitalist, art investor and worldclass DJ. On a typical day you might catch DJ Dave spinning tracks at a friends art opening or donating metric tons of carrots to his favorite charities. Dave is a balanced bunny, he can get crazy at rave or just chill on his patio smoking his pipe. Dave has an ever-growing harem of supermodel bunnies who provide him with hundreds of little ones to love and take care of. It is safe to say that Dave has lived a full life, and he is only getting started.
